chunk_content: 117 • This indicator captures if implementing partners are tracking the HIV status of the OVC that they serve and enrollment in ART for those who are positive. Testing results for OVC who are referred T for testing should be reported under HTS_TST based on the service delivery point where they are E tested. S • This indicator also captures if implementing partners are tracking if the OVC that they serve who T I report to be living with HIV are successfully linked to and have continuity of treatment and care. N ART treatment status should be recorded both at the time of enrollment as well as at regular G intervals at least once during the reporting period. • Since this is not a testing indicator, HIV positivity yield should NOT be calculated based on this indicator. Yield calculations should only be made by testing partners.
